After the plan was marked complete, the user raised a missing skill:

> I think I missed and agent/skill here related to ontology generation. As far as I know, there are open accessible ontology repositories, right. If so, it would make sense to interact with those to include new ontological concepts relevant to the problem under scrutiny/development. what are your thoughts about this new topic that I am bringing here?

